  "texts": [
    "The results are shown in Table II.",
    "The symbol ① represents non-stripped binaries while ② represents stripped binaries.",
    "We first analyze the results of non-stripped binaries (i.e., the data under the column \"①\").",
    "The column \"MVR\" in Table II shows the ability of DeGPT to rename variables.",
    "The MVRs of different codebases vary from 27.0% to 37.0%, with an average MVR of 30.3%."
